column5: I know its a bit late to post this but my fishing partner bailed on me for tomorrow. But I have an extra seat in my hut and was wondering if anyone wants to get out tomorrow? If you don't have gear that's ok I have just about everything you would need. Will be getting on the ice at innisfil beach park at 6am if anyone wants to join me they are more then welcome My cell is 647-519-8965
Have fun my friend... 3 more days of fishing for smiles from Nurses for me !
maybe give you a call in the morning when we get out
Smiles from nurses what's next sponge baths lol
Sounds good Kwan will keep my eyes out for other OFC Members
